text:
Yo Mr. Enthu boy(or Mr. M),
                        Kitne bhi chutiyape krta ho, lekin dil ka mast aur saaf banda h. Koi ni help krne ko hota, lekin tu jrur rhta h humseha. Waise mere bhi 80% IITK ki photos me tu hoga hi. XYZ me bahut masti ki, MNO yaad rhega... likhne ki jrurt ni, kyuki college life ke 80% cheezo me tu saath me hi tha. Kisi se milna ho na ho tujhse to hoga hi, even if we never talk over phone calls ><.  BTW blowback tagda tha, brahman ghuma diya poora :)
